flavor_text_entries.black:
Its lovely scales are described as
rainbow colored. They change color
depending on the viewing angle.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
MILOTIC is said to be the most
beautiful of all the POKéMON.
It has the power to becalm such emotions as anger and hostility to quell
bitter feuding.
flavor_text_entries.sapphire:
MILOTIC live at the bottom of large
lakes. When this POKéMON’s body glows a
vivid pink, it releases a pulsing wave of energy that brings soothing calm to
restless spirits.
flavor_text_entries.emerald:
It is said to live at the bottom of
large lakes. Considered to be the most
beautiful of all POKéMON, it has been
depicted in paintings and statues.
flavor_text_entries.firered:
MILOTIC is breathtakingly beautiful.
Those that see it are said to forget their
combative spirits.

flavor_text_entries.diamond:
When people bicker, it is said to
arise from the depths of lakes to
becalm violent hearts.
flavor_text_entries.pearl:
It is the world’s most beautiful
Pokémon. There are many works of
art featuring MILOTIC.

flavor_text_entries.alpha-sapphire:
Milotic live at the bottom of large lakes. When this

flavor_text_entries.sun:
Milotic has provided inspiration to many artists.
It has even been referred to as the most
beautiful Pokémon of all.
flavor_text_entries.moon:
It lives at the bottom of clear lakes. In times of
war, it shows itself, which soothes people’s
minds and hearts.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-sun:
While Milotic is said to be the most beautiful
Pokémon, Trainers who like Feebas and have
raised it are seemingly disappointed by Milotic.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-moon:

Those who behold its loveliness are said to
have their hearts purified.
